    "We delve into the practical application of LLM-Chatbots as a resource for parents seeking guidance, emphasizing the need to evaluate the precision and effectiveness of their responses in such real-life contexts.",
    "The insights gained from this study are signi cant and could lay the groundwork for incorporating LLM-Chatbots into the management of adolescent health and development.",
